Name: Super Greedy Cat
About the game: Help King Meow to travel the world to find it's missing gold coin! Super Greedy Cat is a platformer where you explore different level with multiple enemies. Do specific challenge to collect Stars at the end of the levels. Each coin gives you a speed boost during 2 seconds which can be cumulated 10 times. Key Features of version 1.0.0: 20 level campaign Steam leaderbard Steam achievements 60 Challenges Roadmap: Level editor
